Chordate/The Protectobots:




The ex-bridge officer remained in a sleep like mode from an overload of 
liquid energon that would give him drunk like qualities later on.

----

Hot Spot helped a stiff Blades out of a CR chamber.  "You alright?"

"Yeah, but next time we fight to the Pit with fighting fair.  Am I the last 
one out?"

"Yeah, I hear you.  There will be some major payback against those damn 
Decepticons.  No, you're the second one out counting myself, looks like 
Groove will be the next one.  We'll wait here until all of us are out and 
then ask for orders and quarters."

"Sounds fine to me."
